                                                     vann:preferredNamespacePrefix "h2kg" ;
                                                     vann:preferredNamespaceUri h2kg: ;
                                                     rdfs:comment """The ontology captures PEMFC catalyst-layer experimental concepts, parameters, properties, measurements, instruments, materials, and related FAIR provenance. It preserves the historic h2kg namespace while improving metadata quality, release readiness, and public documentation.
